<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  lastUpdated="February 2026"
  description="Crawlix Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    At Crawlix, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our desktop SEO crawler application.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Key Point:</strong> Crawlix is a desktop application that runs entirely on your local machine. Your crawl data, reports, and analysis never leave your computer unless you explicitly choose to export or share them.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>License Information:</strong> When you purchase a Pro or Agency license, we collect your email address and payment information through our payment processor (Lemon Squeezy).</li>
    <li><strong>Support Requests:</strong> If you contact us for support, we collect the information you provide in your communications.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>License Validation:</strong> When validating your license, we collect a hardware fingerprint to manage device activations. This fingerprint is anonymized and cannot identify you personally.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Checks:</strong> The application may check for updates, which involves a connection to our servers. No personal data is transmitted during this process.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Information We Do NOT Collect</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Crawl data from websites you analyze</li>
    <li>Reports you generate</li>
    <li>URLs you crawl</li>
    <li>Your browsing history</li>
    <li>Analytics or telemetry from the application</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Process your license purchase and manage your subscription</li>
    <li>Validate your license and manage device activations</li>
    <li>Provide customer support</li>
    <li>Send important updates about the software (security updates, major releases)</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Payment Processor:</strong> Lemon Squeezy processes all payments and handles billing-related data.</li>
    <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
    <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@crawlix.app">privacy@crawlix.app</a>.</p>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. License and billing records are retained for the duration of your subscription plus any legally required retention period.
  </p>

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
  </p>

  <h2>Global Privacy Control (GPC)</h2>
  <p>
    We respect the Global Privacy Control signal. If your browser sends a GPC signal, we will treat it as a valid opt-out request.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Crawlix is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@crawlix.app">privacy@crawlix.app</a></li>
    <li>Website: <a href="https://crawlix.app/contact">crawlix.app/contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</LegalLayout>
